  "body": "There seems to be an issue with hardhat 2.5.0 when using `hardhat node --watch`, when a redeploy is triggered an error about sender not having enough funds comes up\r\n\r\nI've created a minimal repo to reproduce this at https://github.com/rjchow/hardhat-deploy-watch-repro\r\n\r\nTo reproduce, \r\n\r\n1. npm install\r\n2. npx hardhat node --watch\r\n3. wait for it to run\r\n4. modify greeter.sol to trigger a recompile and redeploy\r\n5. error manifests\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/27843274/128367582-3d069227-4a8e-4158-ae09-6b36f65c942d.png)\r\n",
